# Screen Wakelock Detector — project rules

Read [`docs/START_HERE.md`](docs/START_HERE.md) and [`AGENTS.md`](AGENTS.md) every session.

## Milestone workflow

- Work from [`BUILD_PLAN.md`](BUILD_PLAN.md) labels: AGENT / ADB / HUMAN / AUTO
- Spawn **parallel subagents** for `<!-- PARALLEL -->` blocks (see [`docs/FOR_AGENTS.md`](docs/FOR_AGENTS.md))
- **Run until milestone complete** — gate checklists in [`docs/GATES.md`](docs/GATES.md)

## Validate before push

Never push without:

1. `./gradlew lint test assembleDebug`
2. Applicable gate checklist items
3. **`scripts/smoke/m{N}_smoke.sh` exit 0** before archive
4. CHANGELOG `[Unreleased]` + AGENT_MEMORY updated

## Smoke before archive

- **Never** run `archive-completed-tasks.py` without smoke PASS in GATES.md
- Record: `Smoke M{N}: PASS <timestamp> <serial> <version>`

## Git

- Lead agent only commits/pushes per milestone
- Do not start M(N+1) until M(N) gate passed and pushed

## Root (libsu)

- In-app only; command allowlist — no user input in shell
- Document in [`docs/ROOT.md`](docs/ROOT.md)

## Do not edit

- Plan files in uploads/ or external `.plan.md` sources — use BUILD_PLAN.md instead

FOSS, M3, and security rules: see `foss-compliance.mdc`, `design-system.mdc`, `ci-gates.mdc`.
